{"tid":1973181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"湯家驊︰李慧琼仍有主席權力　可繼續主持內會","createTime":"2020-04-15T04:44:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T10:56:43.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":369,"uniUserReply":82,"replies":[{"pid":"0451540d2d12a6ef1cd41a4a076f2795dd296fe4","tid":1973181,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:44:26.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】行會成員湯家驊指出，根據議事規則，內會選出新主席前，上個立法年度的主席仍然有主席的權力，建議李慧琼繼續主持會議，恢復內會運作。<br />\n<br />\n湯家驊：「因為現在是選不到主席，即是上一個會期的主席也繼續是內會主席。既然如此，為何內會主席不去恢復內會運作？選主席可以慢慢選，一個星期選一次也好，一個月選一次也好，選到屆末也選不到是另一回事。但現存主席可以繼續召開內會恢復運作，為何不做呢？」"},{"pid":"b5c063ed3a45008bd22ab0f9397ea94244de3855","tid":1973181,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:44:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=387761\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387761&d=kRIfmd%2Br1GQrfPRU1wEKQAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=b65e73e0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D387761&h=a07d80ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=387761</a>"},{"pid":"d249a1a1cad9bb7fa8438100ec96e9ebec135e13","tid":1973181,"uid":228437,"like":201,"dislike":1,"score":200,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:48:03.000Z","msg":"你返雪廠街啦闔家鏟"},{"pid":"2b746b51b671f0ee696de1a194e0a1e30115e724","tid":1973181,"uid":39383,"like":148,"dislike":0,"score":148,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"咁唔撚使選啦, 終身連任好唔好, 柒頭"},{"pid":"ed0b5ee63c5fe4cf6011d51b54fab34d43faf25f","tid":1973181,"uid":6810,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-15T04:49:44.000Z","msg":"琼子幫手攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"876af0d73e5e00b43ce7df4ff17158c9cf196f90","tid":1973181,"uid":338262,"li